com.github.jonathanxd.iutils.object.specialized

Class EitherObjLong<L>

  • java.lang.Object
    • com.github.jonathanxd.iutils.object.BaseEither
      • com.github.jonathanxd.iutils.object.specialized.EitherObjLong<L>
  • Type Parameters:
    L - Left value.

    public abstract class EitherObjLong<L>
extends BaseEither
    A class which can hold either L or long (in this documentation we call the hold value as present value). Left value (L) may be null even if the value is present.
